    "is_free": true,
    "description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >This is a survival adventure game inspired by Resident Evil 2, but without the horror element.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >The player receives a mission to find treasure, exploring vast stages, solving puzzles, and either avoiding or defeating enemies while trying to escape.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Strategic gameplay is required due to the limited resources and inventory system, offering tension and a sense of challenge without relying on fear.</p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Key Features</h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Puzzle Solving and Treasure Hunting:</strong></p></li></ul><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3280560/extras/02c69640316e41bfa236650c082f0f16.avif?t=1729851357\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3280560/extras_big/02c69640316e41bfa236650c082f0f16.avif?t=1729851357 width=800 height=450 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Players must find hidden treasures and solve puzzles across various stages, with the ultimate goal of escaping.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Combat or Avoidance:</strong></p></li></ul><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3280560/extras/82410153fe3cd1c0964900c61216fc68.avif?t=1729851357\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3280560/extras_big/82410153fe3cd1c0964900c61216fc68.avif?t=1729851357 width=800 height=416 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Throughout the stages, players encounter enemies that can either be defeated or avoided, depending on the situation.</p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Limited Resources:</strong></p></li></ul><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3280560/extras/099597823dbefbe6ff82e7a160be726d.avif?t=1729851357\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3280560/extras_big/099597823dbefbe6ff82e7a160be726d.avif?t=1729851357 width=800 height=506 /></span></p></li></ul><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3280560/extras/c3093fd5138c90a0563463edc51c51db.avif?t=1729851357\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3280560/extras_big/c3093fd5138c90a0563463edc51c51db.avif?t=1729851357 width=800 height=432 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >The number of consumable items, such as bullets, keys, and healing items, is limited, making efficient resource management essential.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Inventory Management:</strong></p></li></ul><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3280560/extras/b409469e3fda4325e01b6d2ed0b4d50c.avif?t=1729851357\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3280560/extras_big/b409469e3fda4325e01b6d2ed0b4d50c.avif?t=1729851357 width=800 height=570 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >With limited inventory space, players must selectively carry important items, and these choices have a significant impact on the game's progression.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Messages from Predecessor Agents:</strong></p></li></ul><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3280560/extras/46be261aa5495195d85179a9a279a240.avif?t=1729851357\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3280560/extras_big/46be261aa5495195d85179a9a279a240.avif?t=1729851357 width=800 height=420 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Scattered across the map are tips left by previous agents. Reading and using this information can be helpful during gameplay.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p></li></ul><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Controller Support</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Gameplay is only available through mouse &amp; keyboard controls.</p>",
